的知友一定一定看清楚问题——是孩子真正喜欢，而让你反复的绘本，而不是扔书单。 做好倾听者，是一个真正好的回答者。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picb.zhimg.com/50/v2-19d0ff1855cb0013b933a1490f303775_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/408094121"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ii4i6sK28nqlCEAMaCDUyOTY1MDQyIO3r2PgFMAA49gNAMXIJNDA4MDk0MTIxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "next": "", "previous": ""}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新"}